Remove Incorrect NVIDIA Driver Packages

First, remove the incompatible driver packages:

Command:
    sudo dnf remove -y akmod-nvidia xorg-x11-drv-nvidia xorg-x11-drv-nvidia-libs xorg-x11-drv-nvidia-cuda-libs

Note:
- At one point, removing `*nvidia*` also affected related components and caused temporary issues
  with audio, internet, and graphics behavior.
- System recovery was done before continuing.
